}}'''世界癌症日'''是每年設於2月4日的国际纪念日，設立世界癌症日的目的是提高人们对[[癌症|癌症]]的认识，鼓励人们预防、发现和治疗癌症，减少因癌症引起的疾病和死亡<ref name="World Cancer Day 2013 Summary">{{Cite web|title=World Cancer Day 2013 One-Pager (English)|url=http://www.worldcancerday.org/background-information|accessdate=2 February 2013|publisher=UICC|archive-date=2014-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140902010449/http://www.worldcancerday.org/background-information}}</ref>。世界癌症日由[[國際抗癌聯盟|國際抗癌聯盟]]（UICC）牵头，以實現2008年通過的《世界癌症宣言》的目标<ref>{{Cite web|title=World Cancer Day|url=https://www.who.int/cancer/world-cancer-day/en/|accessdate=2018-09-09|work=World Health Organization|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204130923/https://www.who.int/cancer/world-cancer-day/en/}}</ref>。[[联合国|联合国]]在这一天會举行纪念活动<ref>{{Cite web|title=International Days|url=https://www.un.org/en/sections/observances/international-days/|date=January 6, 2015|work=www.un.org|access-date=2021-03-27|archive-date=2015-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328001659/https://www.un.org/en/sections/observances/international-days/}}</ref>。
== 历史 ==
2000年2月4日，时任[[联合国教育、科学及文化组织|联合国教育、科学及文化组织]]总干事[[松浦晃一郎|松浦晃一郎]]和时任法国总统[[雅克·希拉克|雅克·希拉克]]在巴黎举行的新千年世界抗癌峰会上签署了《巴黎抗癌宪章》<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://unesdoc.unesco.org/ark:/48223/pf0000119111 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204125247/https://unesdoc.unesco.org/ark:/48223/pf0000119111 }}</ref>，该宪章是为了促进研究、预防癌症、改善癌症患者服务而制定，其中有一条规定《巴黎抗癌宪章》签署的周年纪念日为世界癌症日<ref>{{Cite web|title=World Cancer Day: Why the Fourth of February?|url=https://connection.asco.org/magazine/features/world-cancer-day-why-fourth-february|date=March 19, 2012|work=ASCO Connection|access-date=2021-03-27|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224162156/https://connection.asco.org/magazine/features/world-cancer-day-why-fourth-february}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=World Cancer day 2021: Cancer can be Cured by True Worship|url=https://news.jagatgururampalji.org/world-cancer-day-cure-cancer/|accessdate=2021-02-04|date=2021-02-04|work=S A NEWS|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304222449/https://news.jagatgururampalji.org/world-cancer-day-cure-cancer/}}</ref>。

